使<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68767dc43b4b6afc0fdd918b19d4ac941f57ec76","tid":1629313,"uid":30290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:17:28.000Z","msg":"失民意既情況下仲想打壓市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條仆街真係真心想攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe63ddc89c8a90ba7b03c6e363f22cbcb226dccf","tid":1629313,"uid":204948,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:17:36.000Z","msg":"Mphil就叫學者 縮返入去啦"},{"pid":"5024e5990314e76714abb096b568b67b1662219d","tid":1629313,"uid":208245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c2291eb1ff9507468e06ced991a82e9fda5d3a01","tid":1629313,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:44:43.000Z","msg":"Mr CHAN, Wai-keung<br />\n陳偉強<br />\nBA (H.K. Baptist U.); MPhil (C.U.H.K.)<br />\nwaikeung.chan@cpce-polyu.edu.hk<br />\n教學及學術興趣:<br />\n人文<br />\n社會科學<br />\n研究和學術活動<br />\n陳偉強先生現為香港專上學院講師, 亦是東方日報專欄作家及時事評論員 。他於1973年出生， 先後在香港浸會大學及香港中文大學獲取歷史學學士學位及哲學碩士學位。在加入香港專上學院之前，他曾在香港中文大學、倫敦大學及香港公開大學執教。<br />\n<br />\n除了教學外，陳先生亦醉心學術研究，曾擔任夏威夷大學中國研究中心研究員(Eu Tong Sen Fellow)及倫敦大學歷史研究院研究院士(Scouloudi Fellow)。他發表過多篇學術論文及編撰兩部學術著作。其研究焦點集中在當代中國民族主義、國民教育、香港文化保育及香港政治文化等課題上。<br />\n<br />\n陳先生亦積極投身社區，服務社群, 曾於2008年至2015年間擔仼油尖旺區民選議員，並當選油尖旺區議會公民教育運動統籌委員會主席和食物及環境衛生委員會副主席。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:18:49.000Z","msg":"PhD都冇叫咩撚嘢學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c596152cfc262bff5e8bd952f7ed623e7757732","tid":1629313,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1a3b1e904e600781669ae6b57ed48208fa20445","tid":1629313,"uid":103237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:55:39.000Z","msg":"連PhD都冇得果3皮野仲低人工過藍狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:22:29.000Z","msg":"原來咁少人工架?中環求其一條友人工高過佢。"},{"pid":"8f0122b043ddaa7be73175865eb0b86a6fd95b72","tid":1629313,"uid":316927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:22:51.000Z","msg":"白粉報御用垃圾"},{"pid":"b650c274649ad05b3bec450c022c5df8722a83a9","tid":1629313,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:23:29.000Z","msg":"暴動坐終身，殺警又坐終身，何不殺警？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eca0de018f2cf99b839577200057a3509d058a0","tid":1629313,"uid":276138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:25:24.000Z","msg":"呢個共狗黎 ，之前做區議員， 又係果d無政治聯繫既&ldquo;獨立&rdquo;參選人。"},{"pid":"249716f92b713fa8630bf4da0062df8b697656c3","tid":1629313,"uid":20209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:25:32.000Z","msg":"法官放人？如果係會放人就唔洗要求撤消被捕人士既指控啦"},{"pid":"7b70602eed0420004c58cee467ba2a7f8f3b3572","tid":1629313,"uid":266755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:27:28.000Z","msg":"dklm"},{"pid":"cbda9e71452a8f72991ae591b89b059a7db68747","tid":1629313,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fe5d802ca90f616e04be4e8ff8917f59a03cdf9","tid":1629313,"uid":53026,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:30:27.000Z","msg":"小小一個講師咁臭串？攞邵逸夫獎未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:29:11.000Z","msg":"想入共產黨"},{"pid":"a124705ce2bf6a43c5bfc91af37036b391672359","tid":1629313,"uid":9666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:30:21.000Z","msg":"Hkcc 就話自己係學者收皮啦<br />\n濕鳩學店嚟㗎咋<br />\n你以為你自己真係大學嗰啲prof呀？"},{"pid":"8527952d1d3ef4bf50963ba187339a34775ef3d1","tid":1629313,"uid":31962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:35:06.000Z","msg":"點解從來都唔向問題諗解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咁製造問題就可以止暴制亂？"},{"pid":"b783af810002626d0f999236549fade818c5204c","tid":1629313,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:37:34.000Z","msg":"曲?"},{"pid":"fe2b92c1d8a99f42cce00bc55353fc26a5ac81df","tid":1629313,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:40:23.000Z","msg":"你話重判就重判㗎咩"},{"pid":"d881839954b840766cbdd4989ad1cf26cb1f3e34","tid":1629313,"uid":21090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccdd76ac44c1cef7218fb983e4258cd27b885ce9","tid":1629313,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191005/photo/bkn-20191005125108810-1005_00822_001_02b.jpg?20191005151206\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191005%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191005125108810-1005_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20191005151206&h=779e5547&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府訂立禁蒙面法已經生效，但今日(5日)凌晨各區發生的反修例示威中仍有不少參與者繼續蒙面。學者批評政府立新法多此一舉，因為刑罰更重的暴動罪尚且未能遏止示威潮，不相信刑罰較輕的禁蒙面法能令示威者卻步。學者認為，治亂世用重典，政府應採用較嚴重的暴動罪來止暴制亂，而且法庭應該重判。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191005/photo/bkn-20191005125108810-1005_00822_001_01b.jpg?20191005151206\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191005%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191005125108810-1005_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20191005151206&h=2f80fc6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n理工大學專業及持續教育學院講師陳偉強表示，政府引用《緊急法》只訂立了《禁止蒙面規例》一項新法，但沒有多管齊下，以雷霆萬鈞之勢來平息反修例風波，實在令人失望。他質疑，警方面對成千上萬的蒙面示威者，根本沒有足夠人手和拘留設施，將其全部拘捕，「你拉得一個，拉唔到其他千幾個」。<br />\n<br />\n新法難以執行之餘，陳又指，現時禁蒙面法的最高刑罰是監禁1年，但存在已久的暴動罪最高刑罰是監禁10年，明顯後者的阻嚇性較前者更大，「根本(立禁蒙面法)係多此一舉，依家判10年都仲有咁多人出嚟示威，何況只係判1年」？他認為，問題癥結在於法庭判刑太輕，變相「警察拉人，法官放人」，令法律阻嚇性大打折扣。他促請政府以暴動罪來起訴暴力示威者，法庭亦應考慮社會受影響程度，予以重判。<br />\n<br />\n大律師龔靜儀表示，由於禁蒙面法暫時未有案件可以參考，但法官判案一般會按罪名的量刑起點，考慮案情性質而決定是否需要加刑，得出總刑期後再考慮案件中的減刑因素，例如被告有否認罪及何時認罪等，然後得出最終刑期。<br />\n<br />\n龔又指，假如有參與非法集結的蒙面示威者被捕，其可能干犯的罪行包括「參與非法集結」和「禁蒙面法」，最公平的情況下被告會被同時起訴該兩項罪名，假若全部罪成，法官判刑時亦可能有不同決定，例如全部罪名的刑期同步執行、全部罪名的刑期分期執行，以及全部罪名的部分刑期同期執行，其餘部分則分期執行等，需視乎個別案件的嚴重性而定，不能一概而論。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:42:59.000Z","msg":"你認為政府立蒙面法係想拉人，佢係想緊急法抄家炸"},{"pid":"1df27baedd89056ff78b3ffbe25c1382c6c13749","tid":1629313,"uid":186181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:43:52.000Z","msg":"Who<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061fd310e9dcdffb780deaabb0766cf59fd83460","tid":1629313,"uid":25183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:44:26.000Z","msg":"保險唔賠，藍絲商家佬硬食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65064c59d126012e486934fc42bb4bf4759637db","tid":1629313,"uid":149008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:45:44.000Z","msg":"禿奴返支那食屎"},{"pid":"097f5fa28b68a96e5c766c5cab9ef3cdd7df1358","tid":1629313,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:54:35.000Z","msg":"用蒙面法試水溫姐<br />\n<br />\n之後會立個勁過暴動既法例"},{"pid":"ae147778ea690dad960e344bb02bba0e03c9e4a4","tid":1629313,"uid":321345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:55:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312d07f72205eb7eff47a06d27ddf4ec3c9d6ba0","tid":1629313,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:29:52.000Z","msg":"警察拉人，法官放人<br />\n係因為警察亂拉亂告"}]}